---
title: Mexican Style Cheesy Beef Hash with freshly made guacamole
description: This is a typical potato-based hash with an exciting south-of-the-border twist. Mexican elements come in the form of an expertly blended spice mix and homemade guacamole—of course!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R05_W15_IE_IEXFB0057-3_Main_high-96fcd520.jpg
